+///
+/// Implements CPython's Objects/odictobject.c
+/// OrderedDict maintains insertion order (inherited behavior since Python 3.7)
+///
+/// Reference: cpython/Objects/odictobject.c
+///            cpython/Include/cpython/odictobject.h
